name: EQ-V
details:
5-Band Equalizer Pedal for Guitar and BassThe Skyline EQ-V from Hotone is a 5-band graphic equalizer pedal with a true bypass footswitch designed for use with guitar and bass, providing complete control of your sound and eliminating unwanted feedback. It can also be used as a booster for a multi-dimensional, expanded sound. The pedal includes a zinc alloy outer cover, a large transparent knob for controlling the input level, 5 mini sliders to adjust each of the five EQ bands, and LED indicator lights. The EQ-V is powered by a 9 VDC adapter with a center negative plug (available separately).
Frequencies: 80 Hz, 350 Hz, 720 Hz, 1.6 kHz, 5 kHz with maximum 18 dB boost/cut
True bypass footswitch
Zinc alloy outer cover
Transparent top knob controls input level and 5 mini sliders adjust EQ bands
Cool LED lights
